Change Log for "lock"

1998-10-09	enh	Basel

	Now disables virtual terminals on Linux.

1998-10-04	enh	Basel

	Now locks as many screens as you have.

1998-02-05	enh	Basel

	Now names its window "lock" so that other programs can tell when
	the display's locked. See the code in clock.

1997-10-06	enh	Basel

	Ignores non-alphanumeric "characters", so that pressing Ctrl to
	stop the screen blanking no longer inserts a character. Hides
	the pointer.

1997-10-03	enh	Basel

	Created.
